    <name>Shapefile Writer</name>
    
    <shortDescription>
        Write a Shape file
    </shortDescription>
    
    <fullDescription>
        <intro>This node writes out the input data table into a shape file denoted by an destination location. 
        A projection SRID value also need required to write the shape file.
        The first table must contain a geometry column in GeoJSON format. 
        </intro>
        
        
        <option name="a single coordinate system  value such as WGS84 (SRID 4326)">SRID value</option>
        <option name="Output location">Enter a valid file name or URL. You can select a local file from the "Browse..." dialog. 
</option>
